Privacy Policy
Last updated: April 14, 2024
This Privacy Policy describes how Livity (“we”, “us”, or “our”) collects, uses, and shares your information when you use our application, Livity (the “App”). By using the App, you agree to the collection and use of information by this policy.
Information We Collect
Email Address: We collect your email address to create and manage your account, and to communicate with you regarding important updates or information related to the App.
How We Use Your Information
Email Address: Your email address is used for account management purposes and to communicate with you about updates, new features, or important information related to the App. We do not share your email address with third parties.
Apple Watch Metrics: The metrics collected from your Apple Watch are used within the App to provide insights and recommendations tailored to your health and fitness goals. We do not share this data with third parties. All calculations are performed within the App.
Data Security
We are committed to protecting the security of your information. We implement reasonable security measures to safeguard your personal information against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction.
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes to this policy will be posted within the App, and your continued use of the App after any modifications to the Privacy Policy will constitute your acknowledgment of the modifications and your consent to abide and be bound by the updated Privacy Policy.
Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us at
livityapphelp@gmail.com
